Name: ComponentReference
Description: Reference to a category used in the generation process.

Name: Description
Description: A description of the generation process. Supports multiple language versions of the same content as well as optional formatting of the content.

Name: CommandCode
Description: Structured information used by a system to generate the category.

Name: OtherMaterialReference
Description: External documentation required for creating the generation - for example, a chart or table for defining poverty.

Name: IsDerived
Description: If not a derivation process set this attribute to "false".

Name: Qualification
Description: A qualification for the generation process expressed as a simple string.
